'''Urugomero rwa Rukarara''' ni Urugomero rwa 9.5 MW (12.700) hp) z’amashanyarazi mu [[Rwanda]] . <ref name="Open">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-01-12/rwanda-starts-operating-rukarara-hydropower-plant-ministry-says</ref> <ref>http://allafrica.com/stories/201009220162.html</ref>

== Aho biherereye ==
Sitasiyo y'amashanyarazi iherereye ku mugezi wa Rukarara, mu Karere ka Nyamagabe, mu Ntara y'Amajyepfo y'u Rwanda, hafi 182 kilometres (113 mi) mu majyepfo ashyira uburengerazuba bwa [[Kigali]], umurwa mukuru mu [[Rwanda]] <ref>http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Rwanda_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Nyamagabe%2C%20Southern%20Province%2C%20Rwanda&toplace=Kigali%2C%20Rwanda%2C&dt1=ChIJo3PUuzoawxkRUT6iM5nqPm4&dt2=ChIJl-fYjiWk3BkRyAsdQaU2K_M</ref>

== Incamake ==
Urugomero rwa MW 9,6 rwubatswe mubyiciro byinshi. Icyiciro cya mbere, gifite ubushobozi bwa MW 6.9, cyarangiye muri 2011. Icyiciro cya kabiri, gifite ubushobozi bwa MW 2,2 cyarangiye muri 2014. Amafaranga yo kubaka sitasiyo yose y’amashanyarazi yari miliyoni 13.12 US $, inkunga yatanzwe na guverinoma yu Rwanda, [[Umuryango w’Ubumwe bw’Ibihugu by’i Burayi|Umuryango w’ubumwe bw’ibihugu by’Uburayi]] [https://www.btcctb.org/en/ n’ikigo gishinzwe iterambere ry’Ububiligi] . <ref>http://www.hydroworld.com/articles/2014/06/rwanda-complete-2-2-mw-rukarara-2-small-hydropower-project.html</ref>

== Ibindi bitekerezo ==
Amashanyarazi yatanzwe yimurwa binyuze muri sitasiyo nshya i Rukarara no mu murongo mushya w'amashanyarazi maremare kuva Rukarara kugera Kirinda. <ref>http://www.africanreview.com/energy-a-power/transmission/opec-fund-for-rwanda-power-project</ref>

